Package: gtcheck
Type: Package
Title: Inspect 'gt' Tables for Automated Checking
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sam Parmar
Maintainer: Sam Parmar <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: gtcheck provides functions that inspect gt objects to make it 
    easier to ensure that tables meet expectations. It is similar to ggcheck 
    for ggplot2 objects.
